title: Chicken Pox Translation Spanish
cleaned_text:
Most kids have no problems with the chickenpox vaccine.

It is different than the chickenpox vaccine. Esta es diferente de la vacuna contra la varicela. For example, the chickenpox vaccine may be safer to your unborn baby than getting the infection.

La vacuna contra esta enfermedad se realiza precisamente para desarrollar los anticuerpos necesarios para que las personas no enfermen cuando entran en contacto con el agente infeccioso. Children whose mothers have had chickenpox or have received the chickenpox vaccine are not very likely to catch it before they are 1 year old. More translations in context: vacunado contra]
